data.description: Welcome to 701 Bamboo Drive!  You will love the space offered in this 5 bedroom 2.5 bath home. You are greeted with a two story entry with tons of natural light & nice sized formal dining area featuring lovely windows. Kitchen has  new granite counters, freshly painted cabinets, newly built island & window over the sink. Laundry located just off of the kitchen for convenience. Breakfast area is adjacent to the kitchen & on the way to the oversized family room! Perfect area for friends & family to gather. Primary suite offers generous sized room & bath with garden tub & separate shower. Upstairs find an additional 4 bedrooms & game room! Home has plenty of rooms that offer a flex space for an office or the 5th bedroom. Home sits on an oversized pie shaped lot that is tree lined. No neighbors behind, which makes the backyard very private & quiet. Oversized covered patio area, great for those family gatherings and BBQ’s!
